videos.description: Yang Yang the Panda from Zoo Atlanta selects the Crimson Tide to win the Peach Bowl.
videos.headline: Who does Yang Yang think will win the Peach Bowl?

tracking.trackingName: SEC_NCF Misc (Panda makes Peach Bowl pick) 161231

videos.description: Washington coach Chris Petersen shares his team's preparation for the Chick-fil-A Peach Bowl.
videos.headline: Chris Petersen on Washington's preparation for the Chick-fil-A Peach Bowl

videos.description: Alabama coach Nick Saban discusses his team's preparation for the Chick-fil-A Peach Bowl.
videos.headline: Nick Saban shares Alabama's preparations for the Chick-fil-A Peach Bowl

videos.description: Jake Browning connects with Dante Pettis on a 16-yard touchdown pass to get Washington on the scoreboard first.
videos.headline: Washington opens scoring with 16-yard TD pass

videos.description: Alabama RB Bo Scarbrough won't be denied for an 18-yard touchdown against Washington.
videos.headline: Alabama powers its way into the end zone

videos.description: Anthony Averett strips the ball from John Ross to force the first turnover of the game.
videos.headline: Alabama forces first turnover of game

videos.description: Alabama elects to defer after winning the opening coin toss, and the Crimson Tide leave the field without shaking hands with Washington's players, despite the official's urging.
videos.headline: Alabama refuses to shake hands after coin toss

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Alabama refuses to shake hands after coin toss) 2016/12/31

videos.description: Adam Griffith hits a 41-yard field goal to give Alabama a 10-7 lead against Washington.
videos.headline: Alabama takes its first lead of the game

videos.description: Ryan Anderson intercepts Jake Browning's pass and returns it for a 26-yard Alabama touchdown.
videos.headline: Alabama comes up with pick-six

videos.description: Nick Saban on Alabama's offensive performance so far and defensive adjustments to make for the 2nd half
videos.headline: Nick Saban on Alabama's offensive performance so far and defensive adjustments to make for the 2nd half

videos.description: Alabama strikes late with a pick-six to take a 17-7 lead over Washington through the first half of the Chick-fil-A Peach Bowl.
videos.headline: Alabama momentum stalls in second half

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Alabama carries momentum into second half) 2016/12/31

videos.description: Chris Petersen on how Washington's offense can help out the defense's field position
videos.headline: Chris Petersen on how Washington's offense can help out the defense's field position

videos.description: Bo Scarbrough takes the handoff and goes 68 yards to the end zone to extend Alabama's lead to 24-7.
videos.headline: Scarbrough races 68 yards to the end zone

videos.description: After giving up the opening touchdown to Washington, Alabama scores the final 24 points to roll into the College Football Playoff championship game.
videos.headline: Alabama rolls into CFP championship

videos.description: On 4th and long, Jake Browning throws a pass to the endzone where Alabama's Minkah Fitzpatrick picks it off.
videos.headline: Browning Interception seals Alabama win

videos.description: Alabama coach Nick Saban discusses his team's 24-7 win over Washington.
videos.headline: Saban pleased with Peach Bowl win

videos.description: Alabama's Bo Scarbrough talks with Holly Rowe after having a 180 yard, two-touchdown performance in the 24-7 victory over Washington in the Chick-fil-A Peach Bowl.
videos.headline: Scarbrough looking forward to title game

videos.description: Breaking down Alabama's 24-7 win over Washington in the Peach Bowl
videos.headline: Breaking down Alabama's 24-7 win over Washington in the Peach Bowl

videos.description: Alabama rewarded with the George P. Crumbley Trophy
videos.headline: Alabama rewarded with the George P. Crumbley Trophy

videos.description: Bama players join SEC Nation's Maria Taylor, Tim Tebow and Marcus Spears to have some fun and recap their Peach Bowl victory.
videos.headline: Crimson Tide crash SEC Nation set after Peach Bowl

tracking.trackingName: SEC_NCF Misc (Bama players crash Nation set) 161231

videos.description: Mark May highlights Alabama's defensive touchdown that was the play that changed the game around, and a play that was needed with the Crimson Tide's weak offensive performance.
videos.headline: Defensive touchdown Alabama's biggest spark

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Analysis (Mark May on Alabama win) 2016/12/31 SC

videos.description: Bo Scarbrough rushes for 180 yards and two touchdowns while Alabama adds a pick-six en route to a 24-7 win over Washington in the Chick-fil A Peach Bowl.
videos.headline: Scarbrough, Alabama marches on to CFP Championship

videos.description: SEC Nation's Maria Taylor, Tim Tebow and Marcus Spears talk about RB Bo Scarbrough's dominant performance against the Huskies.
videos.headline: Bo Scarbrough shines in Peach Bowl

videos.description: Alabama DL Jonathan Allen joins SportsCenter and discusses his team's effort against Washington, using the momentum the Crimson Tide had heading into halftime and speaking highly of RB Bo Scarbrough for winning the MVP.
videos.headline: Allen says Bama's defense communicated and executed

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Interview (Allen says Bama's defense communicated and executed) 2016/12/31 ESHEET SC

videos.description: Alabama QB Jalen Hurts joins SEC Network's Laura Rutledge to talk about the Tide's execution in the Peach Bowl and how it feels to play for a national championship.
videos.headline: Hurts: 'We still have work to do'

videos.description: The SEC Nation crew reflects on the LB's performance vs. Washington and why he feels disrespected.
videos.headline: Ryan Anderson named Defensive Player of Peach Bowl

videos.description: Alabama rides its relentless defense to a Chick-fil-A Peach Bowl win, stymieing Washington and turning its mistakes into points.
videos.headline: Bama's defense downright scary in Peach Bowl

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Bama's defense downright scary in Peach Bowl) 2016/12/31 ESHEET ENHL

videos.description: SEC Network's Chris Doering and Clint Stoerner analyze big moments in the Tide's Peach Bowl victory.
videos.headline: Examining key plays in Alabama's win over Washington

videos.description: Alabama shakes off Washington to move on to Tampa for a shot at winning back-to-back national championships.
videos.headline: Alabama keeps on rolling towards another title

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Feature (Alabama-Washington Mini Movie) 2016/12/31 ESHEET SCEU
